						               													<description>Minions' Revolution is a mini board game for 1 to 6 players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It contains a single rules page, three random tables and a print 'n play sheet. Each table contains 6 to 12 covering room's randomizer, treasure and events. The game is very easy to learn and each game lasts less than ten minutes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Minions' Revolution can be played solo using an AI system to manage other monsters trying to take control of the dungeon.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game system itself is single d6 based. Each monster is unique and pre-generated. Each monster has 3 characteristics: fight, run and health. It is an ideal system for players who like to change character at every game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Actions are quickly resolved. The game system works on the principle of save rolls. Miss the roll and lose one health point.&amp;#10;The rules are certainly not perfect. When in doubt, write to me (or find out who is right in arm wrestling).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
